name: Scan or Scam - Cashier Job Simulator
summary:
Scan, weigh, sell! 🛒
Welcome to the checkout counter! Scan the items customers bring up with your scanner 📦🔔, weigh fruits and veggies 🥝⚖️, show off products in the display 🧃✨… and run your shop like a pro! 👔
